<title>ESTONIA: BALTIKA GROUP SALES FORECAST AT 345 MLN KROONS.</title>
<headline>BALTIKA GROUP SALES FORECAST AT 345 MLN KROONS.</headline>
<dateline>TALLINN 1997-08-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Batika group, a clothing manufacturer and retailer, said on Friday that its adjusted turnover forecast for 1997 was 345 million kroons.</p>
<p>In a statement, the company said that the unconsolidated 1997 turnover forecast for Baltika was 216 million kroons.</p>
<p>Baltman, the largest retail firm in Baltika, which has outlets in Estonia, Finland, Latvia and Lithuania expects a 1997 turnover worth 87 million kroons.</p>
<p>-- Tallinn newsroom +372 620 9201/2 reuters@reuters.ee</p>
